This is a simple command-line utility that discovers DigiConnect devices on
a IP network and prints out their MAC and IP addresses.

Originally written by John Kelley (<FirstName> (at) <LastName> (dot) ca).
(http://kelley.ca/wordpress/2008/10/24/digi-connect-me-discovery/)

Slight modifications by:
    - Tomaz Solc    (<FirstName> (dot) <LastName> (at) tablix (dot) org)
    - Andre Miras   (<FirstName> (dot) <LastName> (at) gmail (dot) com)
